Tsuyazaki-cho (津屋崎町) and Fukuma-shi (福間市) merged in 2005 to become Fukutsu-shi.
You can take JR Kagoshima Honsen (鹿児島本線) to Fukuma (福間) Station. Kagoshima honsen goes to major cities like Hakata and Kokura. You can take Seitetsu bus (西鉄バス） to Tsuyazaki-bashi (津屋崎橋).

value: Fukutsu has many different types of birds such as black-faced spoonbill.
